post.description:
导出完整分析报告到 Excel

请求体示例：
```json
{
    "analysis_info": {
        "title": "2025年1月销售分析报告",
        "date": "2025-01-26",
        "data_source": "sales_data.csv",
        "card_counts": {
            "fact": 5,
            "interpret": 3,
            "risk": 2,
            "action": 4
        },
        "summary": "本报告分析了1月销售数据..."
    },
    "cards_by_type": {
        "fact": [...],
        "interpret": [...],
        "risk": [...],
        "action": [...]
    },
    "filename": "sales_analysis_report.xlsx"
}
```
